vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dWibfl4IqKm3fJ5dW46tsPpU2ga.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/wZczqBIX40sD3wb0IlGdYIteAKv.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2304,"height":1296,"file_path":"/4jrdU5p1K8H61Fgmk6pCHEb5LBf.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ckwSFPNTtzqV579qjINWQM56bsk.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/nXOac5JEERbklneBz64RAJ9ianN.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/vpiJMwWu4YAWbnoVZuPjsxPCqRW.jpg","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1772,"height":997,"file_path":"/WoQpLboj2L4hTaWubyR63AMGsk.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/dpBMczaFeaPwkCWf9DnIe4uugOB.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T02:31:04.922+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dopo la morte del fratello, June si trasferisce a Milano e trova conforto in Will, lo studente modello della sua nuova scuola internazionale. Ma quando James, il migliore amico di Will e campione di combattimenti clandestini di MMA, scatena una rivalità che si trasforma in un'attrazione irresistibile, June deve scegliere tra la sicurezza e un amore che sconvolge tutto ciò che pensava di volere."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"After her brother's death, June moves to Milan for a fresh start, finding comfort in Will, the perfect honor student at her new international school. But when his troubled best friend James—hiding a dangerous life in clandestine MMA fights—sparks a rivalry that quickly turns into irresistible attraction, June must choose between safety and a love that upends everything she thought she wanted."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tras la muerte de su hermano, June se muda a Milán para empezar de nuevo. Allí encuentra refugio en Will, el alumno perfecto de su instituto internacional. Pero James, el problemático mejor amigo de Will, que oculta una peligrosa vida en peleas clandestinas de MMA, convierte la rivalidad en una atracción irresistible que obliga a June a elegir entre una vida segura y un amor que lo cambia todo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Amor Demais","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Após a morte de seu irmão, June recomeça a vida em Milão, namorando Will, um cara perfeito da sua nova escola internacional. Mas quando o melhor amigo do rapaz, o perigoso James que participa de lutas clandestinas de MMA, desperta uma rivalidade que rapidamente se transforma numa atração irresistível, June precisa escolher entre a segurança e um amor que transforma tudo que ela pensou que queria."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://press.amazonmgmstudios.com/us/en/original-movies/love-me-love-me","overview":"Après la mort de son frère, June s'installe à Milan pour repartir de zéro et trouve du réconfort en sortant avec Will, l'élève modèle de sa nouvelle école. Mais le meilleur ami de Will, James, adepte de combats clandestins de MMA, attise une rivalité qui se mue en attirance irrésistible. June doit alors choisir entre la sécurité et un amour qui remet en question tout ce qu'elle pensait vouloir."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Love Me, Love Me","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tras la muerte de su hermano, June se muda a Milán para empezar de nuevo y encuentra consuelo en Will, el alumno modelo de su nueva escuela internacional. Pero cuando su conflictivo mejor amigo James inicia una rivalidad que pronto se convierte en una atracción irresistible, June deberá elegir entre la seguridad y un amor que lo pone todo en jaque."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"爱我爱我","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　琼在弟弟离世后搬往意大利，寻求全新的生活。在新就读的精英学校里，她被危险的校园霸凌者詹姆斯吸引，此人还参与地下综合格斗赛，可琼却与詹姆斯的挚友、完美的优等生威尔展开了交往。但表象往往具有欺骗性，琼很快发现，这所学校里的每个人都并非表面看上去的模样，人人都藏着秘密。随着矛盾不断升级，隐藏的真相逐一浮出水面，琼必须做出抉择，弄清自己的真心究竟归向何方。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"รักนะ รักฉัน","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หลังพี่ชายเสียชีวิต จูนย้ายมามิลานเพื่อเริ่มต้นใหม่ เธอได้พบกับความสบายใจในวิล นักเรียนดีเด่นผู้สมบูรณ์แบบในโรงเรียนนานาชาติแห่งใหม่ แต่เมื่อการฟาดฟันกับเจมส์ เพื่อนซี้เกเรของวิล ผู้กุมความลับเรื่องสังเวียนเอ็มเอ็มเอใต้ดิน ได้จุดชนวนกลายเป็นความดึงดูดที่เกินต้านทาน จูนต้องเลือกระหว่างความปลอดภัยที่คุ้นเคย หรือความรักที่จะพลิกผันทุกอย่างที่เคยต้องการไปตลอดกาล"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Kochaj mnie... kochaj mnie","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Po śmierci brata June przenosi się do Mediolanu, by rozpocząć nowe życie. Znajduje ukojenie w Willu, wzorowym uczniu międzynarodowej szkoły. Jednak jego przyjaciel James, zawodnik nielegalnych walk MMA, rozpoczyna rywalizację, która szybko przeradza się w nieodparte przyciąganie. June musi wybrać między bezpieczeństwem a miłością, która stawia na głowie jej dotychczasowe pragnienia."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"사랑해 줘 사랑해 줘","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"오빠의 죽음으로 모든 것을 잃은 준은 상처를 안고 밀라노로 떠나 국제학교로 전학한다. 그곳에서 만난 모범생이자 완벽한 연인인 윌에게서 안정을 찾지만, 비밀스럽고 위험한 불법 격투 경기에 몸담은 절친 제임스와의 갈등은 서서히 금지된 설렘으로 바뀌어 가고, 준은 안전한 삶과 모든 것을 뒤흔드는 사랑 사이에서 흔들린다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Love Me, Love Me","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nach dem Tod ihres Bruders fängt June in Mailand neu an und findet Trost bei Will, dem perfekten Schüler auf ihrer neuen internationalen Schule. Aber als sein bester Freund James, der ein gefährliches Leben mit MMA-Kämpfen verbirgt, eine Rivalität entfacht, die zu unwiderstehlicher Anziehung wird, muss June sich zwischen Sicherheit und einer Liebe entscheiden, die ihre Wünsche auf den Kopf stellt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"תאהבו אותי, תאהבו אותי","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"לאחר מותו של אחיה, ג׳ון עוברת למילאנו כדי לפתוח דף חדש, ומוצאת נחמה בוויל, תלמיד מצטיין ומושלם בבית הספר הבין-לאומי החדש שלה. אך כשחברו הטוב והמיוסר, ג׳יימס, שמסתיר חיים מסוכנים של קרבות אמנויות לחימה משולבות מחתרתיים, מצית יריבות שהופכת במהרה למשיכה שאי אפשר לעמוד בפניה, ג׳ון נאלצת לבחור בין ביטחון לבין אהבה שמערערת את כל מה שחשבה שהיא רוצה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"愛我愛我","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在哥哥去世後，茱恩前往米蘭的國際學校讀書展開新生活，並在校內與完美模範生威爾的邂逅中找到情感上的慰藉。然而，這一切在她遇上威爾最好的朋友詹姆士後都將改變。詹姆士放浪不羈卻又魅力十足，背後還藏著一段參與地下綜合格鬥比賽的刺激人生。在兩人最初的敵意逐漸化為難以抗拒的吸引力時，茱恩也面臨感情的難題，被迫要在熟悉的安全感與一段顛覆一切的愛情之間做出抉擇。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"أحبّني... أحبّني","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"بعد فقدان شقيقها، تبدأ \"جون\" حياة جديدة في \"ميلانو\". في مدرستها الدولية، تنجذب إلى \"ويل\"، الطالب المثالي الذي يمنحها شعوراً بالأمان. لكن مشاركة \"جيمس\"، صديق \"ويل\" الغامض والسري في نزالات الفنون القتالية المختلطة غير القانونية، يشعل منافسة تتحوّل سريعاً إلى انجذاب خطير. بين الأمان وحب يهدّد كل قناعاتها، تجد \"جون\" نفسها أمام خيار سيغيّر مصيرها."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Love me, love me","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nebaren heriotzaren ostean, June hutsetik hasiko de Milanen, eta aringarria izango du Will, bere nazioarteko eskolako ikasle saiatua. Baina bere lagun min nahigabetsu Jamesek -MMA borroka klandestino arriskutsuetan sartuta dagoena- erakarpen jasanezina sentiaraziko dion lehia pizten duenean, Junek segurtasunaren eta bere ustez nahi zuen guztia aldatzen duen maitasunaren artean aukeratu beharko du."},"name":"euskera","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Basque"},{"data":{"title":"أحبّني... أحبّني","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"بعد فقدان شقيقها، تبدأ \"جون\" حياة جديدة في \"ميلانو\". في مدرستها الدولية، تنجذب إلى \"ويل\"، الطالب المثالي الذي يمنحها شعوراً بالأمان. لكن مشاركة \"جيمس\"، صديق \"ويل\" الغامض والسري في نزالات الفنون القتالية المختلطة غير القانونية، يشعل منافسة تتحوّل سريعاً إلى انجذاب خطير. بين الأمان وحب يهدّد كل قناعاتها، تجد \"جون\" نفسها أمام خيار سيغيّر مصيرها."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Amb la mort del seu germà, la June començar de nou Milà i surt amb en Will, l'estudiant d'honor perfecte de la nova escola internacional. Però el seu millor amic problemàtic James -que amaga una vida perillosa en combats clandestins d'MMA-, encén una rivalitat que es transforma en una atracció irresistible, i la June ha de triar entre la seguretat i un amor que capgira tot el que creia voler."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"June se po bratrově smrti stěhuje do Milána, aby začala znovu. Útěchu nachází u Willa, premianta na mezinárodní škole, kam nově chodí. Když se však jeho problémový nejlepší přítel James, tající nebezpečný život v nelegálních zápasech MMA, pustí do soupeření, rychle se měnícího v neodolatelnou přitažlivost, musí si June vybrat mezi bezpečím, nebo láskou převracející vše, po čem myslela, že touží."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Efter brorens død starter June på en frisk i Milano og finder trøst i den perfekte Will på sin nye internationale skole. Da hans problematiske bedste ven, James, som skjuler et farligt liv som hemmelig MMA-kæmper, udløser en rivalisering, der forvandler sig til en uimodståelig tiltrækning, må June vælge mellem tryghed og en kærlighed, der vender op og ned på alt det, hun troede, hun ønskede sig."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"爱我 爱我","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"哥哥去世后，琼移居米兰重新开始生活，在新国际学校与完美优等生威尔相恋，从中获得慰藉。然而，当威尔那位问题重重的挚友詹姆斯--暗藏着参与地下综合格斗赛的危险生活的男孩--引发的敌对火花迅速演变为无法抗拒的吸引力时，琼必须在安稳的生活与颠覆她所有认知的爱情之间作出抉择。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na de dood van haar broer verhuist June naar Milaan. Ze vindt troost bij Will, een voorbeeldige leerling op haar internationale school. Als zijn getroebleerde beste vriend James, die een gevaarlijk leven leidt met MMA-gevechten, een rivaliteit ontketent die omslaat in onweerstaanbare aantrekkingskracht, moet June kiezen tussen veiligheid en liefde die alles wat ze dacht te willen op zijn kop zet."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Αγάπα Με Αγάπα Με","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Μετά τον θάνατο του αδερφού της, η Τζουν μετακομίζει στο Μιλάνο για να του νέου της σχολείου. Αλλά ο ανήσυχος κολλητός του, ο Τζέιμς - που κρύβει μια επικίνδυνη ζωή με αγώνες ΜΜΑ - πυροδοτεί μια αντιπαλότητα που γρήγορα μετατρέπεται σε ακαταμάχητη έλξη. Η Τζουν πρέπει να διαλέξει ανάμεσα στην ασφάλεια και σε έναν έρωτα που ξεπερνάει ό,τι πίστευε πως ήθελε ως τώρα."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Après la mort de son frère, June déménage à Milan. Elle trouve du réconfort auprès de Will, l'élève modèle de sa nouvelle école. Mais lorsque James, son meilleur ami, un garçon tourmenté qui participe à combats clandestins, déclenche une rivalité qui se transforme en une attirance irrésistible, June doit choisir entre la sécurité et un amour qui bouleverse tout ce qu'elle pensait vouloir."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Veljensä kuoleman jälkeen June muuttaa Milanoon aloittaakseen uuden elämän. Hän ilmoittautuu kansainväliseen eliittikouluun, jossa hän löytää lohtua seurustelemalla Willin, koulun täydellisen huippuoppilaan, kanssa. Mutta Junen haurasta vakautta horjuttaa tulenarka vihanpito Willin parhaan ystävän Jamesin kanssa. Kauna muuttuu vastustamattomaksi vetovoimaksi."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tras a morte de seu irmán, June múdase a Milán para empezar de cero. Atopa consolo en Will, un estudante perfecto do novo colexio internacional. James, o seu amigo problemático, que oculta unha vida perigosa de pelexas clandestinas, desata unha rivalidade que se converte en atracción irresistible. June debe escoller entre a seguridade e un amor que trastorna todo o que cría querer."},"name":"Galego","iso_639_1":"gl","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Galician"},{"data":{"title":"ラブミー・ラブミー","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ジューンは兄を亡くした後、新たな人生を求めてミラノへ移り住み、エリート校であるインターナショナルスクールに転校する。そこで彼女は学校の優等生であるウィルに安らぎを見いだす。しかし、親友のジェームスがウィルにライバル心を抱かせる。ジェームスは問題を抱えていて、危険な地下格闘技の世界に身を置いていた。ジェームスの抗いがたい魅力を前に、ジューンは平穏な愛と、自分が望んでいると思っていたすべてを覆す愛との間で選択を迫られる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"ಲವ್ ಮಿ ಲವ್ ಮಿ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ತನ್ನ ಸಹೋದರನ ಮರಣದ ನಂತರ, ಜೂನ್ ಹೊಸ ಜೀವನ ಪ್ರಾರಂಭಿಸಲು ಮಿಲಾನ್‌ಗೆ ತೆರಳುತ್ತಾಳೆ, ತನ್ನ ಹೊಸ ಅಂತರರಾಷ್ಟ್ರೀಯ ಶಾಲೆಯಲ್ಲಿನ ಅದ್ಭುತ ವಿದ್ಯಾರ್ಥಿಯಾದ ವಿಲ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ನೆಮ್ಮದಿ ಕಂಡುಕೊಳ್ಳುತ್ತಾಳೆ. ಆದರೆ ಎಂಎಂಎ ಪಂದ್ಯಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಅಪಾಯಕಾರಿ ಜೀವನವನ್ನು ನಡೆಸುತ್ತಿರುವ ಅವನ ಸಮಸ್ಯಾತ್ಮಕ ಆತ್ಮೀಯ ಗೆಳೆಯ ಜೇಮ್ಸ್ ಜೊತೆಗಿನ ಅವಳ ಪೈಪೋಟಿ ತಡೆಯಲಾಗದ ಆಕರ್ಷಣೆಯಾಗಿ ಬದಲಾದಾಗ, ಜೂನ್ ತಾನು ಬಯಸಿದ ಎಲ್ಲವನ್ನೂ ಬುಡಮೆಲು ಮಾಡುವ ಪ್ರೀತಿ ಹಾಗೂ ಸುರಕ್ಷತೆಯ ನಡುವೆ ಆರಿಸಿಕೊಳ್ಳಬೇಕು."},"name":"?????","iso_639_1":"kn","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Kannada"},{"data":{"title":"लव मी लव मी","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"अपने भाई की मौत के बाद, जून नई शुरुआत के लिए मिलान जाती है और उसे नए इंटरनेशनल स्कूल में एक बेहतरीन छात्र विल में सुकून मिलता है। पर जब उसका परेशान सबसे अच्छा दोस्त जेम्स - जो चोरी-छिपे एमएमए फाइट्स में खतरनाक ज़िंदगी जी रहा है - एक ऐसी होड़ शुरू करता है जो जल्दी ही एक ज़बरदस्त आकर्षण में बदल जाती है, तो जून को सुरक्षा और एक ऐसे प्यार के बीच चुनना पड़ता है जो उसकी सोची हुई हर चीज़ को बदल देता है।"},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Szeress, szeress!","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A bátyja halála után June Milánóba költözik, új életet kezd, és vigaszra talál Willben, az új nemzetközi iskolájának eminens tanulójában. De amikor Will problémás barátja, James - aki veszélyes életet él, és titkos MMA-harcokban vesz részt - rivalizálást szít, amely gyorsan ellenállhatatlan vonzalommá alakul, June-nak választania kell a biztonság és a szerelem között, amely felforgatja terveit."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Setelah kematian kakaknya, June pindah ke Milan untuk memulai kembali. Ia menaruh hati kepada Will, pelajar teladan di sekolah internasional barunya. Namun, setelah sahabat Will, James-yang terlibat pertarungan MMA rahasia-memicu persaingan yang segera berubah menjadi ketertarikan yang tak terbendung, June harus memilih di antara rasa aman dan cinta yang mengguncang segala yang ia inginkan."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Efter broderns död flyttar June till Milano för att börja om. På hennes nya internationella skola finner hon trygghet hos Will, den perfekta toppeleven. Men när hans plågade kompis James, som lever ett farligt dubbelliv med hemliga MMA-matcher, väcker en rivalitet som snabbt övergår i attraktion, ställs June inför ett val mellan trygghet och en kärlek som kullkastar allt hon trodde sig vilja ha."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Iubește-mă, iubește-mă","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"După moartea fratelui ei, June se mută la Milano pentru un nou început și găsește alinare în Will, elevul-model de la școala ei internațională. Totul se schimbă când James, cel mai bun prieten al lui, implicat în lupte MMA clandestine, declanșează o rivalitate care se transformă rapid într-o atracție periculoasă. June are de ales între siguranță și o iubire care îi dă peste cap toate așteptările."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Etter brorens død flytter June til Milano for en ny start og finner trøst hos Will, toppeleven på den internasjonale skolen. Men da hans plagede venn James - som skjuler et farlig liv med hemmelige MMA-kamper - skaper en rivalisering som raskt blir til uimotståelig tiltrekning, må June velge mellom trygghet og en kjærlighet som snur opp ned på det hun trodde hun ville ha."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"ലവ് മി ലവ് മി","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"സഹോദരന്റെ മരണ ശേഷം, ജൂൺ ഒരു പുതിയ ആരംഭത്തിനായി മിലാനിലേക്ക് പോയി, അവിടെ അന്ത രാഷ്ട്ര സ്കൂളിലെ നല്ലവനായ ഉന്നതവിദ്യാർഥി വില്ലിൽ ആശ്വാസം കണ്ടെത്തുന്നു. എന്നാൽ അവന്റെ നിഷേധിയായ സുഹൃത്ത്, രഹസ്യമായി എംഎംഎ പോരാട്ടങ്ങളിൽ അപകടകര ജീവിതം നയിച്ചിരുന്ന ജെയിംസുമായി ഏറ്റുമുട്ടിയപ്പോൾ, അത് ആകർഷണമായി മാറുന്നു. ജൂൺ സുരക്ഷിതത്വത്തിനും, തന്റെ സങ്കൽപ്പത്തിനപ്പുറത്തെ സ്നേഹത്തിനും തമ്മിൽ തെരഞ്ഞെടുക്കേണ്ടിയിരിക്കുന്നു."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"ml","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Malayalam"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"June berpindah ke Milan selepas abangnya mati untuk mulakan hidup baharu dan bercinta dengan Will, pelajar contoh sempurna di sekolah antarabangsa baharunya. Apabila James, rakan baik Will yang bermasalah, menyembunyikan kehidupan berbahaya dalam pertarungan MMA-mencetuskan persaingan yang menjadi tarikan sukar ditolak, June terpaksa memilih antara keselamatan dan cinta yang mengubah pendiriannya."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"లవ్ మీ లవ్ మీ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"తన సోదరుడి మరణం తర్వాత, జూన్ తన కొత్త అంతర్జాతీయ పాఠశాలలో పరిపూర్ణమైన గౌరవ విద్యార్థి విల్‌లో ఓదార్పును పొందుతూ, కొత్త ప్రారంభం కోసం మిలన్‌కు వెళ్లింది. కానీ రహస్య ఎంఎంఏ పోరాటాలలో ప్రమాదకరమైన జీవితాన్ని దాచిపెట్టిన సమస్యాత్మకమైన విల్ బెస్ట్ ఫ్రెండ్ జేమ్స్‌తో శత్రుత్వం నిలువరించుకోలేని ఆకర్షణగా మారుతుంది, జూన్ భద్రత ఇంకా ఆమె కోరుకున్న ప్రతిదానిని తలకిందులు చేసే ప్రేమ మధ్య ఎంచుకోవాల్సి వస్తుంది."},"name":"తెలుగు","iso_639_1":"te","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Telugu"},{"data":{"title":"Sev Beni Sev Beni","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kardeşinin ölümünden sonra yeni bir başlangıç için Milano'ya taşınan June, yeni uluslararası okulundaki kusursuz onur öğrencisi Will'de huzur bulur. Ama Will'in gizli MMA dövüşlerine katılan sorunlu arkadaşı James'le başlayan rekabet, hızla karşı konulmaz bir çekime dönüşür. June güvenli olanla istediğini sandığı her şeyi altüst eden aşk arasında seçim yapmak zorundadır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"லவ் மீ லவ் மீ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"அண்ணன் இறந்ததும், ஜூன் புதிய தொடக்கத்திற்காக மிலனுக்குப் போக, அங்கே புதிய சர்வதேச பள்ளியில் சிறந்த மாணவன் வில்லிடம் ஆறுதல் காண்கிறாள். ரகசிய எம்எம்ஏ சண்டைகளில் ஆபத்தான வாழ்க்கை வாழும்-அவனது பொல்லாத உற்ற தோழன் ஜேம்ஸ்-​​விரைவில் தவிர்க்கமுடியாத ஈர்ப்பாக மாறும் ஒரு போட்டியைத் தூண்ட, ​​ஜூன் பாதுகாப்புக்கும் அவள் விரும்புவதாக நினைத்த அத்தனையும் தலைகீழாக மாற்றும் காதலுக்கும் இடையே தேர்வு செய்ய வேண்டும்."},"name":"தமிழ்","iso_639_1":"ta","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Tamil"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Após a morte do irmão, June recomeça a vida em Milão, encontrando conforto com Will, o aluno perfeito da sua nova escola internacional. Mas quando o melhor amigo dele, James (que combate em lutas de MMA clandestinas), desperta uma rivalidade que rapidamente se torna numa atração irresistível, June tem de escolher entre a segurança e um amor que vira do avesso tudo o que ela pensava que queria."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Люби меня, люби меня","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"После смерти брата Джун переезжает в Милан, чтобы начать жизнь с чистого листа. Она находит утешение в Уилле, отличнике из её новой международной школы. Но когда его лучший друг Джеймс, скрывающий свою опасную жизнь за подпольными боями без правил, вызывает у Уилла соперничество, которое быстро перерастает в непреодолимую симпатию, Джун приходится выбирать между безопасностью и любовью, которая переворачивает всё её представления о жизни."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Обичай ме, обичай ме","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"След смъртта на брат си, Джун се мести в Милано, за да започне начисто. В новото си международно училище тя намира утеха в Уил — перфектния отличник с безупречна репутация. Но когато неговият проблемен най-добър приятел Джеймс, който крие опасен живот в нелегални ММА битки, предизвиква съперничество, прерастващо в неудържимо привличане, Джун трябва да избере между сигурността и любов, която преобръща всичко, в което е вярвала."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Yêu Em Nhé","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sau khi mất anh trai trong một tai nạn, June (Mia Jenkins) quyết định rời quê nhà để bắt đầu lại ở Milan – thành phố của ánh đèn, thời trang và những cảm xúc mới. Trong ngôi trường quốc tế nơi mọi thứ đều xa lạ, cô gặp Will (Pepe Barroso) – chàng học sinh gương mẫu, điềm đạm và có vẻ như nắm giữ mọi câu trả lời mà cô đang tìm kiếm. Nhưng rồi James (Luca Melucci) xuất hiện – người bạn thân của Will, cũng là kẻ mang trong mình bóng tối của những trận đấu MMA bí mật và quá khứ không mấy yên bình.  Giữa Will an toàn và James nguy hiểm, June dần bị cuốn vào một vòng xoáy cảm xúc mà chính cô cũng không ngờ tới. Tình yêu, nỗi sợ và sự mất mát hòa trộn, khiến mọi ranh giới giữa đúng – sai, an toàn – đam mê trở nên mờ nhạt. Tại Milan, nơi mỗi góc phố đều ẩn chứa một câu chuyện, June phải tự tìm ra đâu mới là điều trái tim mình thật sự khao khát."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":944824,"adult":false,"title":"A","video":false,"overview":"Single-channel video installation commissioned by Public Art Development Trust, London.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1213,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/7LhPaLmbRJ8NzovDxCYFD6kss9G.jpg","release_date":"2002-09-25","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"A","original_language":"en"},{"id":333824,"adult":false,"title":"Don't Hug Me I'm Scared 4","video":false,"overview":"The fourth instalment in the surreal Don’t Hug Me I’m Scared videos in which the three returning characters enter a sinister digital world through their computer.","genre_ids":[27,14,16,10402,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3013,"vote_count":96,"poster_path":"/ijM51fcGVIo6uTyqon00ZLQIT0T.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-31","vote_average":7.651,"backdrop_path":"/A1xDYIRUymJ0bs5cyXjxFOyVjVu.jpg","original_title":"Don't Hug Me I'm Scared 4","original_language":"en"},{"id":758982,"adult":false,"title":"Men","video":false,"overview":"Cleo lives in Marseilles and works as a waitress in a waterfront dive. A stranger entices her into coming to Paris to take dancing lessons, but instead she is taken to a baron, who betrays her. In spite of this inauspicious start, Cleo becomes a successful and renowned actress, but her feelings about men have never recovered. She loathes them and uses them only for the money they offer her, which she then hands over to a penniless girl.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5969,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/5bFV9ANLjvI6x7J96HLRTUOCA53.jpg","release_date":"1924-05-04","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/tKFkRw8vd2Gf86ZBTaZMoTuYy7R.jpg","original_title":"Men","original_language":"en"},{"id":30790,"adult":false,"title":"Six Reasons Why","video":false,"overview":"In a desolate place called the Badlands, four men stand off with guns drawn, their fingers ready at the trigger. Among them are a fugitive seeking redemption, a son out to avenge his father's murder, a loyal servant with a secret and a murderous criminal hired to kill with a vengeance. This is their story...in a place where revenge, deception and cruelty are a way of life.","genre_ids":[28,878,37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4562,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/7Hvd9DxJIys0lORQmf8syEIMzMi.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-15","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/2hfNL0MtSSQLc4LAFzG4aQQB3rL.jpg","original_title":"Six Reasons Why","original_language":"en"},{"id":568300,"adult":false,"title":"BTS World Tour: Love Yourself in Seoul","video":false,"overview":"Shot at the Olympic Stadium in Seoul during the BTS World Tour ‘Love Yourself’ to celebrate the seven members of the global boyband and their unprecedented international phenomenon.","genre_ids":[10402,99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8486,"vote_count":452,"poster_path":"/1u0rtWPgYfAWmqveXOsQDvMRODD.jpg","release_date":"2019-01-26","vote_average":8.233,"backdrop_path":"/8GXkzHTvuj3ftethkrqW330LJKz.jpg","original_title":"러브 유어셀프 인 서울","original_language":"ko"},{"id":70153,"adult":false,"title":"La terza stella","video":false,"overview":"In a small italian town everyone's waiting for the event of the year: the living chess game with a near town.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2519,"vote_count":73,"poster_path":"/qvXSfOjuOUTMY6qLS7WNWDXPsWE.jpg","release_date":"2005-03-11","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/sbAhS3iJytWUHgwBpHocqtybPpF.jpg","original_title":"La terza stella","original_language":"it"},{"id":43137,"adult":false,"title":"Teacher's Pet","video":false,"overview":"A rugged city editor poses as a journalism student and flirts with the professor.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7678,"vote_count":99,"poster_path":"/nScpsAfMBj0ehlisTOuwivnulH5.jpg","release_date":"1958-04-01","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/yu8B4OYoVwDMYi7ozuke8FGrKvq.jpg","original_title":"Teacher's Pet","original_language":"en"},{"id":807223,"adult":false,"title":"Re-Births","video":false,"overview":"A documentary film depicting five intimate portraits of migrants who fled their country of origin to seek refuge in France and find a space of freedom where they can fully experience their sexuality and their sexual identity: Giovanna, woman transgender of Colombian origin, Roman, Russian transgender man, Cate, Ugandan lesbian mother, Yi Chen, young Chinese gay man…","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4309,"vote_count":50,"poster_path":"/dC3y4IJW0yClaKBaMqXxVQ6nOXr.jpg","release_date":"2017-12-01","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/njPvpcxJu8PBNl5eVe8R6YF8SHJ.jpg","original_title":"Re-naissances","original_language":"fr"},{"id":5558,"adult":false,"title":"The Phantom of Liberty","video":false,"overview":"This Surrealist film, with a title referencing the Communist Manifesto, strings together short incidents based on the life of director Luis Buñuel. Presented as chance encounters, these loosely related, intersecting situations, all without a consistent protagonist, reach from the 19th century to the 1970s. Touching briefly on subjects such as execution, pedophilia, incest, and sex, the film features an array of characters, including a sick father and incompetent police officers.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8138,"vote_count":320,"poster_path":"/f6cON5ebistPm6AS1XcZZMmKpIi.jpg","release_date":"1974-09-10","vote_average":7.442,"backdrop_path":"/Ai3fiCnWzHl3bL4CZQQ1pt2uiOU.jpg","original_title":"Le Fantôme de la liberté","original_language":"fr"},{"id":812434,"adult":false,"title":"Star","video":false,"overview":"Giacomo is a low-level actor and voice actor with a great passion for acting. After another disappointing audition he has one last chance to get the part assigned","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6115,"vote_count":38,"poster_path":"/4oObDGDhycViadrRCC2XJwwXAcR.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-19","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Star","