al_title":"The Reader","original_language":"en"},{"id":8067,"adult":false,"title":"A Life Less Ordinary","video":false,"overview":"A couple of angels, O'Reilly and Jackson, are sent to Earth to make sure that their next supervised love-connection succeeds. They follow Celine, a spoiled rich girl who has just accidentally shot a suitor and, due to a misunderstanding, is kidnapped by janitor Robert. Although Celine quickly frees herself, she stays with Robert for thrills. O'Reilly and Jackson pursue, hoping to unite the prospective lovers.","genre_ids":[14,35,10749],"popularity":1.015,"vote_count":483,"poster_path":"/tk7WNEwLZepFU2yPIIkRuQOO0Q9.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-24","vote_average":6.127,"backdrop_path":"/78fqm4OGHe4a1Sl1WhX12pV8Ocr.jpg","original_title":"A Life Less Ordinary","original_language":"en"},{"id":470691,"adult":false,"title":"Esmeralda","video":false,"overview":"It was the first film version of the Hunchback of Notre Dame.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.8091,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/yPohMvllKNZoDNd7ODCsBsXkWZM.jpg","release_date":"1905-12-01","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Esmeralda","original_language":"fr"},{"id":277296,"adult":false,"title":"Vice and Virtue","video":false,"overview":"1944 : Occupied France. Juliette (Vice) is Wehrmacht General Bamberg's mistress and enjoys a privileged life. Her younger sister  Justine (Virtue) is about to marry Jean who is in the Resistance and come to Juliette for help. Both sisters end up at \"la Commanderie\", where Juliette becomes SS Colonel Schonberg's mistress and Justine is detained with other pretty girls who must satisfy the sexual needs of high-ranking nazi officials. Inspired by \"Justine ou les infortunes de la vertu\" by the marquis de Sade","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.1858,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/4s6aUGjsjP3FkiC98HzWmXvA0FR.jpg","release_date":"1963-03-01","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/zK30zKTI5QqXK43GGO73NH3d72m.jpg","original_title":"Le Vice et la Vertu","original_language":"fr"},{"id":8092,"adult":false,"title":"This Boy's Life","video":false,"overview":"When a son and mother move to Seattle in hopes for a better life, the mother meets a seemingly polite man. Things go south when the man turns out to be abusive, endangering their lives. As the mother struggles to maintain hope in an impossible situation, the son has plans to escape.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.8552,"vote_count":1056,"poster_path":"/pRMSZfen1Cv1eqwDbtxCBpBqxnU.jpg","release_date":"1993-04-09","vote_average":7.125,"backdrop_path":"/6N6VUUR1gzbCkiGpQzvRREv3Od1.jpg","original_title":"This Boy's Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":661539,"adult":false,"title":"A Complete Unknown","video":false,"overview":"New York, early 1960s. Against the backdrop of a vibrant music scene and tumultuous cultural upheaval, an enigmatic 19-year-old from Minnesota arrives in the West Village with his guitar and revolutionary talent, destined to change the course of American music.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":5.1723,"vote_count":1369,"poster_path":"/llWl3GtNoXosbvYboelmoT459NM.jpg","release_date":"2024-12-25","vote_average":7.081,"backdrop_path":"/kcCy5tKTe6WepVQ6SQaSewpmoCj.jpg","original_title":"A Complete Unknown","original_language":"en"},{"id":277509,"adult":false,"title":"Miracle in Four Days","video":false,"overview":"Dvorak's Symphony No. 9, \"From the New World\" wafts through a hospice recreation room. Sitting at the grand piano is a young girl, Chiori, with a prodigious ability to play any piece of music after one hearing. Keisuke Kisaragi whose career was abruptly cut short when he jumped in front of a bullet fired by a crazed gunman. The nerves in one hand were severed but he saved the life of Chiori. The tragic incident takes the lives of Chiori's parents, however, and Keisuke becomes her guardian. Not long after their return to Japan, Keisuke discovers Chiori's musical gift.","genre_ids":[10749],"popularity":0.4078,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/isw3Fi8hG6U7D53KidUT1apM9VV.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-04","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/hy9JsbY4skGKK5Ofs6GhgbprjMM.jpg","original_title":"四日間の奇跡","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8289,"adult":false,"title":"Gorky Park","video":false,"overview":"Police Inspector Renko tries to solve the case of three bodies found in Moscow's Gorky Park but finds his attempts to solve the crime impeded by his superiors. Working on his own, Renko seeks out more information and stumbles across a conspiracy involving the highest levels of the government.","genre_ids":[53,80,18,9648],"popularity":1.315,"vote_count":334,"poster_path":"/xQFH7XlMk8pLPDzK5XVEj5McsRm.jpg","release_date":"1983-12-15","vote_average":6.323,"backdrop_path":"/dO8qUkabhQwBy8lPGawtvWQkdKd.jpg","original_title":"Gorky Park","original_language":"en"},{"id":8326,"adult":false,"title":"Holes","video":false,"overview":"After being wrongfully convicted for stealing a pair of shoes, Stanley Yelnats is sent away to Camp Green Lake, a boys detention facility where inmates are forced to dig holes all day in the hot desert sun as a form of character building. But Stanley and the other boys start to unravel a mystery, linked with the camps tough-as-nails warden —and possibly Stanley’s family itself.","genre_ids":[12,10751,18,35],"popularity":3.73,"vote_count":1509,"poster_path":"/o2Dm2mcE1qW8vT0bpsJO5OMBbqa.jpg","release_date":"2003-04-18","vote_average":6.895,"backdrop_path":"/cVMK2k0Wbs8DV3IK5sS4ziVenrI.jpg","original_title":"Holes","original_language":"en"},{"id":8619,"adult":false,"title":"Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World","video":false,"overview":"After an abrupt and violent encounter with a French warship inflicts severe damage upon his ship, a captain of the British Royal Navy begins a chase over two oceans to capture or destroy the enemy, though he must weigh his commitment to duty and ferocious pursuit of glory against the safety of his devoted crew, including the ship's thoughtful surgeon, his best friend.","genre_ids":[12,18,10752],"popularity":4.3795,"vote_count":3438,"poster_path":"/s1cVTQEZYn4nSjZLnFbzLP0j8y2.jpg","release_date":"2003-11-14","vote_average":7.181,"backdrop_path":"/zMHyNxNt4zhL939XX8QLBW3gWfu.jpg","original_title":"Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World","original_language":"en"},{"id":8649,"adult":false,"title":"Bringing Out the Dead","video":false,"overview":"Once called \"Father Frank\" for his efforts to rescue lives, Frank Pierce sees the ghosts of those he failed to save around every turn. He has tried everything he can to get fired, calling in sick, delaying taking calls where he might have to face one more victim he couldn't help, yet cannot quit the job on his own.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":3.0113,"vote_count":1191,"poster_path":"/gE2Q8mL0m0EA6HakRyc92uzSPJn.jpg","release_date":"1999-10-22","vote_average":6.607,"backdrop_path":"/A1V1suhllQJ1CTrKpCulcM7mjyj.jpg","original_title":"Bringing Out the Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":8680,"adult":false,"title":"The Shell Seekers","video":false,"overview":"Penelope Keeling, a sixty-four-year-old daughter of a famous artist, reflects on her life, and the fate and choices that defined it, when she arrives in the Mediterranean to stay with her headstrong daughter. Shifting through time, and falling into place like the pieces of a jigsaw, the truth of Penelope's rich, heartbreaking and surprising life unfolds.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.384,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/y7oxk0TY47vpJ1v2kcnYak0GKkX.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-18","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/3OqHYx2QlUQxbXx6TsCAenICQd7.jpg","original_title":"The Shell Seekers","original_language":"en"},{"id":661475,"adult":false,"title":"Apinan vuosi","video":false,"overview":"A young student seeks direction in his life to counterbalance the studies through female adventures.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.3868,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/2OnmxCt66lXG1MuSky901gwGruq.jpg","release_date":"1983-11-11","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/7XvomNV2M9UqZEa87IRk69F441R.jpg","original_title":"Apinan vuosi","original_language":"fi"},{"id":8417,"adult":false,"title":"Süss, the Jew","video":false,"overview":"Nazi historical drama about Duke Karl Alexander of Württemberg and his treasurer Süß Oppenheimer.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.3165,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/3fN1p4OY7Mi0zXQqMJvCdhRwEYs.jpg","release_date":"1940-09-24","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":"/4msV23h4lRFXQoOUUL8Oc0XTcxt.jpg","original_title":"Jud Süß","original_language":"de"},{"id":8434,"adult":false,"title":"Summer Things","video":false,"overview":"Two couple of friends, one very rich, the other almost homeless, decide to go on Holiday. Julie, a single mother, joins them too. Once at seaside, it starts a complicate love cross among them that will involve also a transsexual, a jealous brother, a Latin Lover and another nervous stressed couple. Not to mention about the daughter of one of them that is secretly in Chicago with one of her father's employees... At the end of the summer, all of them will join the same party...","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.5336,"vote_count":102,"poster_path":"/laV4Xo5O1COZefAFPJLFZ28pkYS.jpg","release_date":"2002-03-04","vote_average":5.809,"backdrop_path":"/azkp4brPsmzJiyKw5ExkPDrVpWA.jpg","original_title":"Embrassez qui vous voudrez","original_language":"fr"},{"id":277352,"adult":false,"title":"The Passionate Adventure","video":false,"overview":"A rich man leaves his wife, poses as a coster, and saves a factory girl from a crook.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.133,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/h1PZ9Wk4336u4vYcJup6CJtERt7.jpg","release_date":"1924-07-01","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/e5C3lPya6prhtbXzMw1N0jgakc2.jpg","original_title":"The Passionate Adventure","original_language":"en"},{"id":277364,"adult":false,"title":"Promise at Dawn","video":false,"overview":"A single mother raises her son in impossible circumstances first in Leningrad, then Krakow, and then France, and is over-ambitious about him but never gives in.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1868,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/olkNCkEhhUiRuwMt6hcwxuchGf8.jpg","release_date":"1970-11-25","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/symqYH29cghJJ9QlV4uHtUi5W51.jpg","original_title":"Promise at Dawn","original_language":"en"},{"id":661436,"adult":false,"title":"An Accident","video":false,"overview":"In the 1980s, the building themes were transformed into bipolar moral dilemmas involving overly ambitious individuals who wanted to excel at any cost. The hero is the head of a demolition crew that demolishes large buildings, initially a sympathetic young man who, in the pursuit of career and accolades, begins to transgress the boundaries of what was then called socialist morality and legality. He gradually finds himself at odds with the principles of ordinary but honest people. The narrative's bland, proclamatory film is closely connected to its time of creation, and there are hardly any more timeless insights to be found.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2402,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/iFKRA8kCddfN0B23EXbSW3sOgI4.jpg","release_date":"1986-09-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Havárie","original_language":"cs"},{"id":8338,"adult":false,"title":"Blindness","video":false,"overview":"When a sudden plague of blindness devastates a city, a small group of the afflicted band together to triumphantly overcome the horrific conditions of their imposed quarantine.","genre_ids":[18,9648,878,53],"popularity":6.034,"vote_count":1341,"poster_path":"/deBsx5IxyqCC217j3VY24TkkE0Z.jpg","release_date":"2008-05-14","vote_average":6.512,"backdrop_path":"/sN0czEtCT1jEFQVajWBsKwdFBKm.jpg","original_title":"Blindness","original_language":"en"},{"id":8741,"adult":false,"title":"The Thin Red Line","video":false,"overview":"The story of a group of men, an Army Rifle company called C-for-Charlie, who change, suffer, and ultimately make essential discoveries about themselves during the fierce World War II battle of Guadalcanal. It follows their journey, from the surprise of an unopposed landing, through the bloody and exhausting battles that follow, to the ultimate departure of those who survived.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":4.9213,"vote_count":3223,"poster_path":"/seMydAaoxQP6F0xbE1jOcTmn5Jr.jpg","release_date":"1998-12-23","vote_average":7.445,"backdrop_path":"/hsDyfAk2ml82IrpPC4AHvxvuTsn.jpg","original_title":"The Thin Red Line","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt36331860","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q137786118","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148690,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"+16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","release_dates":[{"note":"Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2026-02-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","release_dates":[{"note":"Pr